narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take this course if you want to learn a lot about music theory in a short period of time. Students enter the class at very different starting levels, but as someone who knew basically nothing about technical music theory, I was able to actively participate in class.
Like it sounds, an intro to music theory. Very relaxed and still informative. Definitely recommend!
This is a great class that anyone interested in music should take. It can be difficult if you really have no knowledge of music whatsoever but still look into this class.
